Product Description: Wenger retained its distinct identity after the takeover by Victorinox Group in 2005. The precision, functionality, thoughtfulness & attention to detail is what underlines the Wenger collection of watches and travel gear which draws on a winning combination of Swiss engineering & reliability. Created in modern designs & using high-grade material, Wenger products are for those who want to count on a Swiss brand at a reasonable cost.We invariably focus on quality, always innovating and adding much joy to ensure that our designs will become your best buddy while travelling. So, if you are looking for a lightweight yet durable suitcase, a backpack or a travel accessory with several cool features and extra packing space, we promise you’ll find one that ticks all of your boxes within our range! So, let's start packing, shall we?Whether packing for everyday routine, vacation time, college or office, or a getaway trip with your friends, our backpacks ensure you're well-equipped and on-trend. We have a quality backpack for the style-savvy traveller in you. Ergonomically contoured shoulder straps. Fully padded laptop compartment. Numerous storage and accessory pockets. Comfortably soar hands-free throughout your day with all your belongings safely stowed in your Wenger backpack. So be ready to roll, because we've got a bag for you!What sets us apart?Creativity redefinedDynamic, contemporary, stylish and loaded with features, there's no limit to where you can go with the Skyport laptop backpack. Featuring protective compartments for your tech & an essentials organizer with an RFID-blocking pocket, it's a bag built for the future.StorageAirflow back padding keeps wearer cool & Shock-absorbing shoulder straps for maximum comfort. CaseBase stabilizing platform keeps the bag standing upright.Stay OrganizedSide access Triple Protect padded 16'' laptop pocket with dedicated 12'' tablet pocket. Essentials organizer with RFID protection keeps power cords, chargers & business cards safe, neat & accessible. Keep your laptop & tablet secure in its own convenient pocket.Read moreKey FeaturesTravel SmoothEasily slip the backpack over your luggage's telescopic handle with its built-in add-a-bag panel or trolley strap.Dimensions & MaterialSize   28 x 31 x 46 cmCapacity   26 lMaterial  PolyesterAgile. Up-to-date. Swiss heritage.Wenger, a renowned Swiss Company since 1893, has a history developed by a passion that combines the reliability & precision of Swiss quality with innovative designs.Read more
